#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/97sWWWBtdgoATYPXMTRko6629OI.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="Joe, 17 ans, est sur le point de sortir d’un centre fermé pour mineurs délinquants. Si son juge approuve sa libération, il ira vivre en autonomie. Mais l'arrivée d'un nouveau jeune, William, va remettre en question son désir de liberté." year="2023-05-03" director="Zeno Graton" actors="Khalil Ben Gharbia, Julien de Saint Jean, Eye Haïdara, Jonathan Couzinié, Samuel Di Napoli, Matéo Bastien, N’landu Lubansu, Amine Hamidou, Terry Ngoga, Aurélien Vandenbeyvanghe",FR - Le paradis (2023)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1417187.mkv&play_token=F9JmXGSRly&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/uDCeELWWpsNq7ErM61Yuq70WAE9.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="When teenage Priscilla Beaulieu meets Elvis Presley at a party, the man who is already a meteoric rock-and-roll superstar becomes someone entirely unexpected in private moments: a thrilling crush, an ally in loneliness, a vulnerable best friend." year="2023-10-27" director="Andrew M. Robinson, Sofia Coppola, Roman Coppola, Aric Dupere" actors="Cailee Spaeny, Jacob Elordi, Ari Cohen, Dagmara Dominczyk, Tim Post",Priscilla (2023)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1407178.mkv&play_token=wGJAMvFqcN&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/mUvikzKJJSg9khrVdxK8kg3TMHA.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="When her scientist ex-boyfriend discovers a portal to travel through time -- and brings back a 19th-century nobleman named Leopold to prove it -- a skeptical Kate reluctantly takes responsibility for showing Leopold the 21st century. The more time Kate spends with Leopold, the harder she falls for him. But if he doesn't return to his own time, his absence will forever alter history." year="2001-12-25" director="James Mangold, Nicholas Mastandrea, Amy Lauritsen, Jennifer Truelove, Sheila Waldron" actors="Meg Ryan, Hugh Jackman, Liev Schreiber, Breckin Meyer, Natasha Lyonne",Kate & Leopold (2001)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1390396.mkv&play_token=1pHnho1KeY&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/n1el846gLDXfhOvrRCsyvaAOQWv.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="Abandoned by her family, Kya raises herself all alone in the marshes outside of her small town. When her former boyfriend is found dead, Kya is instantly branded by the local townspeople and law enforcement as the prime suspect for his murder." year="2022-07-14" director="Olivia Newman, Andrew Shepherd, Stephen E. Hagen, David Bush" actors="Daisy Edgar-Jones, Taylor John Smith, Harris Dickinson, David Strathairn, Michael Hyatt",Where the Crawdads Sing (2022)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1390423.mkv&play_token=t3juTItOCH&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/sP5f85ziKthDrAyXOwoBlnpPmNv.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="Atteinte de la maladie d'Alzheimer, Allie vit en maison de retraite. Chaque jour, Noah lui lit le même livre. Il s'agit du carnet où Allie a consigné sa propre histoire, lorsqu'elle a appris sa maladie. Pour ne pas oublier ses sentiments, elle a écrit, et Noah, inlassablement, lui relit ses propres mots. A travers eux, on la découvre dans les années trente, éperdument amoureuse d'un jeune homme, Noah, que sa mère fera tout pour éloigner d'elle, sa situation n'étant pas jugée assez bonne. Après des années de séparation, à la fin de la Seconde Guerre mondiale, Allie s'apprête à épouser un avocat. Lorsque, par le journal, elle apprend le retour de Noah, l'envie lui prend de le revoir. Echappant à une vie de convenance, les deux jeunes gens se retrouvent et découvrent que leur amour est resté intact. Ils passeront le reste de leur vie ensemble, jusqu'à ce que la mémoire les sépare." year="2004-06-25" director="Nick Cassavetes" actors="Rachel McAdams, Ryan Gosling, Gena Rowlands, James Garner, Sam Shepard, Joan Allen, James Marsden, David Thornton, Kevin Connolly, Starletta DuPois",FR - N'oublie jamais (2004)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1390404.mkv&play_token=1VJXR9kBOc&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

