#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/kgUk1wti2cvrptIgUz0VTAtSF6w.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="Adèle's life is changed when she meets Emma, a young woman with blue hair, who will allow her to discover desire, to assert herself as a woman and as an adult. In front of others, Adele grows, seeks herself, loses herself, finds herself." year="2013-10-09" director="Frédéric Alexandre, Bahijja El Amrani, Antoine Fromental, Monya Galbi, Auriane Lacince" actors="Léa Seydoux, Adèle Exarchopoulos, Salim Kéchiouche, Aurélien Recoing, Catherine Salée",Blue Is the Warmest Color (2013)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1289066.mkv&play_token=MQ9KrDjE6t&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/xO9h6o4LGagbnvwql41hL9tBcrm.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="1916. Julien Delaunay is reported missing in action during the Great War. His wife, Julie, refuses to believe he is dead. 1919. When a photo of an amnesic drifter appears in the press, Julie immediately recognizes him as her beloved husband. They are reunited and, little by little, she helps him to fall in love with her again. Until another woman claims to be the man’s real wife…" year="2023-04-05" director="Guillaume Bureau, Joseph Bellot, Judith Dozières" actors="Louise Bourgoin, Leïla Bekhti, Karim Leklou, Jean-Charles Clichet, Ghislain de Fonclare",Loving Memories (2023)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1289053.mkv&play_token=wWQt7MBuhw&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/11CkMVD0dPjhAZPaf0u9VfS46lw.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="A man tries to make his wife fall in love with him again, after waking up in an alternate reality where she never knew him." year="2019-01-18" director="Matthieu de la Mortière, Lisa-Nina Rives, Hugo Gélin" actors="François Civil, Joséphine Japy, Benjamin Lavernhe, Camille Lellouche, Amaury de Crayencour",Love at Second Sight (2019)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1289076.mkv&play_token=oYBDdjEzvr&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/vBOioZKaGacNtx8G7qZeTPqemk7.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="Diane is a well-known lawyer, divorced for three years. She loses her mobile telephone and receives a call from the person who finds it. That person is Alexandre, a charming man and the perfect gentleman. They make a connection over the phone and agree to meet up the following day. But when Alexandre arrives, there's a surprise in store when Diane discovers he is only 4' 6' tall. From that moment on, Diane tries to overcome the prejudices of society and her own fears to experience the best time of her life..." year="2016-05-04" director="Laurent Tirard" actors="Jean Dujardin, Virginie Efira, Cédric Kahn, César Domboy, Stéphanie Papanian",Up for Love (2016)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1289090.mkv&play_token=mf331AFEI1&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/tFuMLNU3IeWvNMaasJwsDkqbR3T.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="A la fin des années soixante, deux familles émigrent en Israël et se retrouvent voisines dans un minuscule village perdu au milieu de nulle part. L'une vient du Maroc et l'autre de l'Inde. Hormis un rêve, ces gens n'ont rien en commun.  Loin de leurs habitudes et de leurs influences culturelles, ils tentent de reconstruire leur monde. Obligées de cohabiter, les deux communautés se jaugent et tentent d'exister par ce qui les différencie. De malentendus en préjugés, la route vers l'harmonie s'annonce aussi tortueuse que surprenante." year="2004-06-06" director="Avi Nesher" actors="Liraz Charhi, Netta Garti, Jean Benguigui, Parmeet Sethi, Krutika Desai Khan, Ruby Porat Shoval, Nati Ravitz, Aure Atika, Rotem Abuhab, Israel Katorza",FR - Au bout du monde à gauche (2004)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1276511.mp4&play_token=DNzoW3qs5M&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/7InKwVFgvIgfwuPKd0C3R9OeoN7.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="As a patriarchal family yearns for the birth of a son to continue their family line, their youngest son secretly joins an erotic dance theatre and falls for its transgender starlet." year="2022-11-18" director="Saim Sadiq, Sana Jafri, Hyra Basit, Qasim Abbas, Tashish Habib" actors="Ali Junejo, Rasti Farooq, Alina Khan, Sarwat Gilani, Salmaan Peerzada",Joyland (2022)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1276522.mkv&play_token=KA5SD7I5LP&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/gcR1Ce6f2gqRxk2WjzRiparANjf.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="When she fails to meet an item on his list of requirements for a bride, Julia Thistlewaite is jilted by London’s most eligible bachelor, Mr. Malcolm. Feeling humiliated and determined to exact revenge, she convinces her friend Selina Dalton to play the role of his ideal match. Soon, Mr. Malcolm wonders whether he’s found the perfect woman...or the perfect hoax." year="2022-07-01" director="Emma Holly Jones, Jill Dempsey, Stephen Fuller, Christine Dilworth, Ross Ferguson" actors="Freida Pinto, Ṣọpẹ́ Dìrísù, Zawe Ashton, Oliver Jackson-Cohen, Theo James",Mr. Malcolm's List (2022)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1276530.mkv&play_token=57q2uC9WdD&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/tgVBMIiJczfBWINRRd9yxE8ESln.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="The imagined life of one of the world’s most famous authors, Emily Brontë, as she finds her voice and writes the literary classic Wuthering Heights. Explore the relationships that inspired her – her raw, passionate sisterhood with Charlotte and Anne; her first aching, forbidden love for Weightman and her care for her maverick brother whom she idolises." year="2022-10-14" director="Frances O'Connor" actors="Emma Mackey, Fionn Whitehead, Oliver Jackson-Cohen, Alexandra Dowling, Gemma Jones",Emily (2022)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1275617.mkv&play_token=XwgHLgg6VA&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/fzQN7YcIgboMavMMwrOTaqz8agm.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="Bill is an ailing larger-than-life father being taken care of by his son Sam, who has returned home to care for him. While home, Sam falls for a local woman, Kate. At the same time, Bill starts to fall for her mom, Tina." year="2022-11-11" director="Darren Le Gallo, Benjamin M. Dessecker" actors="Jake Hoffman, Schuyler Fisk, Sissy Spacek, Dustin Hoffman, Henry Thomas",Sam & Kate (2022)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1275631.mkv&play_token=DkjIHMyL46&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/6rdzOA9fpkKrDRaBdCMMZ1abeOn.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="Adrian is a Hollywood paparazzi assigned to get photos of a very elusive star, Parker Bennett. Little does she know, she'll get her chance when they both end up at the same BNB in the mountains of NC." year="2022-03-15" director="Elizabeth Snoderly, Nathan Burton" actors="Lexi Giovagnoli, Benedict Mazurek, Victoria Nicole Dresden, Jennifer Adams, Rachel McCubbin",Snapshot of Love (2022)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1275632.mkv&play_token=M0ZH4bAshF&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/wperP8EmDlClErBF8zEdmMGNqKm.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="Former professional ballet dancer Jenna works with NHL star Ryan Cooper to help him recover from an injury using ballet as therapy, and as they grow close, he helps her mend her injured heart. But when it’s time for Ryan to return to the ice and leave Jenna and her small, Connecticut town, they both must consider the paths they want to take and just maybe, love will find its way." year="2021-01-02" director="Kevin Fair" actors="Alexa PenaVega, Luke Macfarlane, Nolen Dubuc, Andrew Dunbar, Heather-Claire Nortey",Taking a Shot at Love (2021)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1273377.mkv&play_token=2gwPgpcEUe&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/iMmRJ3pwrKuH5vBhcdDplzivmIU.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="'A Couple' is a film about a long term relationship between a man and a woman. The man is Leo Tolstoy.  The woman is his wife, Sophia. They were married for 36 years, had 13 children nine of whom survived.  Each kept a diary. Although they lived together, in the same house, they wrote letters frequently to each other.  Leo Tolstoy insisted that they read their diaries aloud to guests at dinner parties.  The Tolstoy’s were also a dysfunctional couple, arguing frequently and being very unhappy with each other while occasionally enjoying passionate moments of reconciliation. The film is Sophia’s monologue about the joys and struggles of their life together, loosely drawn from their letters to each other and their diary entries." year="2022-10-19" director="Frederick Wiseman" actors="Nathalie Boutefeu",A Couple (2022)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1272227.mkv&play_token=g5TmOBvnUP&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/4eqt7ScP8T04gi1P1yI2EYJa9bv.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="Walter Orsini aime faire des grands gestes et parler fort, un peu. Il aime la pêche, la cuisine et les bons vins, beaucoup. Il aime Paul et Jacques, ses amis d'une vie, passionnément. Il aime surtout Clémence, sa fille de 20 ans, à la folie. Mais il n'aime pas le mensonge, mais alors pas du tout. «Dans la vie, on se dit tout» voilà ce qu'il déclare à qui veut l'entendre et même aux autres... Mais il est bien seul à respecter ce principe. Aussi, comment Walter, le fort en gueule, va-t'il réagir quand il découvrira que ceux qu'il aime tant lui mentent effrontément?" year="2013-01-29" director="François Prévôt-Leygonie, Stéphan Archinard" actors="Gérard Lanvin, Jean-Hugues Anglade, Wladimir Yordanoff, Ana Girardot, Zabou Breitman, Natacha Lindinger, Jean-Pierre Lorit, Jean-François Stévenin, Aladin Reibel, Alexia Barlier",FR - Amitiés sincères (2013)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1267584.mkv&play_token=Xmbw8NKcEq&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/d0dcVRrRvfOZi1jDrVsw4pVQ945.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="Laura and Harrison have the picture-perfect romance built on the foundation of a shared love of music. After a deadly accident, Laura gets the chance to save the love of her life when she discovers that their mixtape can transport her back in time." year="2022-06-16" director="Anna Humphries, Greg Björkman" actors="Clara Rugaard, Lewis Pullman, Danny Glover, Lyrica Okano, Christina Chang",Press Play (2022)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1266637.mkv&play_token=zgLzlDb0U1&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/89MSouMUpdC66DsoO189csChV3Z.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="Superficiel et trop gâté, Kyle, 17 ans, est le garçon le plus populaire de son lycée. Obsédé par son image et sa notoriété, il va s'en prendre à la victime de trop... Pour s'amuser, Kyle cherche à humilier Kendra, une fille gothique de sa classe que la rumeur dit être une sorcière. La jeune fille décide de lui donner une bonne leçon et lui jette un sort qui le transforme en un monstre aussi hideux à l'extérieur qu'il l'est à l'intérieur." year="2011-01-21" director="Daniel Barnz" actors="Alex Pettyfer, Vanessa Hudgens, Mary-Kate Olsen, LisaGay Hamilton, Neil Patrick Harris, Dakota Johnson, Erik Knudsen, Peter Krause, David Francis, Gio Perez",FR - Sortilège (2011)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1266638.mp4&play_token=KacPWzBMOy&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/yNxNtEb5PelTqH9PpLIcnWyhvWz.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="Algeria, the 1930s. Younes is nine years old when he is put in his uncle's care in Oran. Rebaptized Jonas, he grows up among the Rio Salado youths, with whom he becomes friends. Emilie is one of the gang; everyone is in love with her. A great love story develops between Jonas and Emilie, which is soon unsettled by the conflicts troubling the country." year="2012-09-12" director="Alexandre Arcady" actors="Nora Arnezeder, Fu'ad Aït Aattou, Anne Parillaud, Vincent Perez, Anne Consigny",What the Day Owes the Night (2012)
