#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/nyB5BeSNJUcWwKN7ypCMjbvnarq.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="Adrienne is trying to decide whether to stay in her unhappy marriage or not, and her life changes when Paul, a doctor who is travelling to reconcile with his estranged son, checks into an inn where she is staying." year="2008-09-26" director="George C. Wolfe" actors="Diane Lane, Richard Gere, Christopher Meloni, Viola Davis, Becky Ann Baker",Nights in Rodanthe (2008)
