#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/6gWQsU4Fmpy5JrXxjrBoeyGfU31.jpg" group-title="|FR| WESTERN" tvg-type="movie" description="Legendary Lawman and Gunslinger Wild Bill Hickok, is tasked with taming the wildest cow-town in the West, while delivering his own brand of frontier Justice and infamous gunfighter's reputation as the fastest draw in the West is put to the test" year="2017-07-07" director="Timothy Woodward Jr." actors="Luke Hemsworth, Trace Adkins, Bruce Dern, Cameron Richardson, Kaiwi Lyman, Kris Kristofferson, Hunter Fischer, Peter Sherayko, Jason Lively, Bertrand-Xavier Corbi",FR - Hickok  (2017)
