#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/6sG7VAXuZSkdEV2BfE9GI82V1wn.jpg" group-title="|FR| PRIME +" tvg-type="movie" description="On vacation with her gal pals, Lacey's friend Janice is found dead. The other women tell the police she must have fallen, but Lacey is sure they are each covering up a deadly secret that they'll do anything to protect." year="2025-03-07" director="Damián Romay, Taylor Jewell Harris" actors="Kristi Murdock, Lesa Wilson, Alex Trumble, Charlotte Hemmings, Lydia Chandler",FR - Deadly Girls Trip (2025)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1926160.mkv&play_token=ZOvs3ej9qL&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/xIkBEP788zO54h0UlEKqPJTYahb.jpg" group-title="|FR| PRIME +" tvg-type="movie" description="Yonathan, expert en montres de luxe au quotidien monotone, voit sa vie basculer lorsqu’il s’associe à Éric, receleur et escroc. Fasciné par le train de vie d'Éric, Yonathan perd toute mesure. Tout s’accélère quand, pour répondre à une commande d'Éric, Jo, cambrioleur de génie, vole cinq chefs-d’œuvre au Musée d’Art Moderne de Paris en 2010." year="2025-04-30" director="Jeremy Mazza, Dominique Baumard, Laure Donnadieu, Jeanne Fontaine-Sarda" actors="Sofiane Zermani, Melvil Poupaud, Steve Tientcheu, Julia Piaton, Nitsa Benchetrit",FR - Les Règles de l'art (2025)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1916990.mkv&play_token=falcIssURx&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/93XDwOGPFh4HJEMmOSSrWL29tOM.jpg" group-title="|FR| PRIME +" tvg-type="movie" description="McWalter, a legendary American elite agent, is falsely accused of a series of attacks all around the globe. Determined to clear his name, he goes on the run to solve the mystery, thwart a earthwise conspiracy, and save the world…" year="2025-09-12" director="Simon Astier, Andreas Meszaros, Augustine Girard, Aurélie Platroz" actors="Yvick Letexier, Géraldine Nakache, William Lebghil, Vincent Dedienne, François Berléand",FR - McWalter (2025)
