#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/5Oz39iyRuztiA8XqCNVDBuy2Ut3.jpg" group-title="|FR| PRIME +" tvg-type="movie" description="Une femme se réveille sur une planète lointaine et découvre que l'équipage de sa station spatiale a été sauvagement tué. Elle doit alors décider si elle peut faire confiance à l'homme envoyé à sa rescousse." year="2025-03-20" director="Flying Lotus" actors="Eiza González, Aaron Paul, Iko Uwais, Kate Elliott, Beulah Koale, Flying Lotus",FR - Ash (2025)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1842720.mkv&play_token=Tv6sUl9TaX&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/3DJusG45vG0487EplZH1Xrq508Z.jpg" group-title="|FR| PRIME +" tvg-type="movie" description="Dans la petite ville de Malegaon, où seul le cinéma permet de s'évader, le cinéaste amateur Nasir Sheikh rallie ses amis pour réaliser un film pour et par les habitants de Malegaon. Dans ce récit poignant sur l'amitié et le septième art, la passion l'emporte sur les petits budgets, l'ingéniosité sur les défis et les rêves suscitent l'espoir, insufflant une nouvelle vie à la ville." year="2025-02-27" director="Reema Kagti" actors="Adarsh Gourav, Shashank Arora, Vineet Kumar Singh, Anuj Singh Duhan, Saqib Ayub, Pallav Singgh, Manjiri Pupala, Muskkaan Jaferi, Anmol Kajani, Gyanendra Tripathi",FR - Superboys of Malegaon (2025)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1841696.mkv&play_token=UF2yLqDohw&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/rEgAdJtf8S8JgUG2NJoWiRvpTz.jpg" group-title="|FR| PRIME +" tvg-type="movie" description="As a heat wave brings a Marseille neighbourhood to the boil, three roommates gleefully meddle in the lives of their neighbours from their balcony. Until a late night drink turns into a bloody affair." year="2024-11-15" director="Noémie Merlant, Pauline Morel, Marie Zoubian, Alice Barsby" actors="Souheila Yacoub, Sanda Codreanu, Noémie Merlant, Lucas Bravo, Nadège Beausson-Diagne",The Balconettes (2024)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1834494.mkv&play_token=nQt2IGJMYR&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/xMr2wApG65RUVGfoX8xq7Gqs1XS.jpg" group-title="|FR| PRIME +" tvg-type="movie" description="The son of a wealthy Haitian presidential candidate has just been kidnapped. The kidnappers are demanding a hefty ransom. Doc and Zoe are two amateur gangsters - and soccer freaks - who must deliver the young man to their ruthless boss. Impulsive Zoe accidentally kills the candidate’s son. Faced with a terrible fate for killing their hostage, Doc and Zoe stumble upon Patrick and his nine-month-pregnant wife, Laura. The young couple must, at all costs, catch a flight out of Haiti to give birth in the US to get citizenship for their baby. Patrick’s great misfortune is that he looks ex- actly like the senator’s dead son. In the midst of a heated election and a Barça-Real classico match, Doc and Zoe find themselves at the center of a political conspiracy." year="2024-01-22" director="Bruno Mourral, Alexandra Kan, Guillaume Leuillet, Thomas Simoen" actors="Jasmuel Andri, Rolapthon Mercure, Anabel Lopez, Ashley Laraque, Gessica Généus",Kidnapping Inc. (2024)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1834493.mkv&play_token=1mzxy0IP7m&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

