#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/aKrwq3HeyFcl5MXb7tcsileoF9I.jpg" group-title="|FR| PRIME +" tvg-type="movie" description="Une femme décide de résoudre le problème du voyage dans le temps afin de revenir en arrière et d'être la personne qu'elle a toujours voulu être." year="2024-09-20" director="Bernardo Britto" actors="Mary-Louise Parker, Ayo Edebiri, Carlos Jacott, Hannah Pearl Utt, Chris Witaske, Fern Katz, Steven Maier, Jennifer Bassey, Maddison Bullock, Riley Fincher-Foster",FR - Omni Loop (2024)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1750442.mkv&play_token=EVm90nnK0K&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/9HFQsvBPCra3P8vIzBB5I0Vuce8.jpg" group-title="|FR| PRIME +" tvg-type="movie" description="In order to earn her trust fund, Evie is tasked with granting Christmas wishes to the people who saved her life on the night of her birth. To aid in her cause, she employs Kyle, a handsome local attorney, to track down those who helped and attempts to secretly learn what they might want while maintaining her anonymity. With Christmas fast approaching, the heiress and the attorney can't resist falling for each other's charms as they ramp up their gift giving efforts. But as time ticks down, will she be able to accomplish the mission and grant all of the wishes by Christmas Eve?" year="2024-11-14" director="Jason Bourque, Mimi Crowe, Eddy Hardy" actors="Taylor Cole, Kevin McGarry, Sarah-Jane Redmond, Eric Keenleyside, Rachel Hayward",FR - A Reason for the Season (2024)
