#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/9WrMmjdZvpxLQh1tCQ9tOd1asOb.jpg" group-title="|FR| NETFLIX JEUNESSE FAMILLE" tvg-type="movie" description="When the four Willoughby children are abandoned by their selfish parents, they must learn how to adapt their Old-Fashioned values to the contemporary world in order to create something new: The Modern Family." year="2020-04-22" director="Kris Pearn" actors="Will Forte, Maya Rudolph, Alessia Cara, Terry Crews, Martin Short, Jane Krakowski, Seán Cullen, Ricky Gervais, Fiona Toth, Islie Hirvonen",FR - The Willoughbys  (2020)
