#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/6b6tqchq0ELFwEqCAQKpglxEDi6.jpg" group-title="|FR| GUERRE" tvg-type="movie" description="During the warring period of the three kingdoms, ancient China is in turmoil. To unify the country, general Cao Cao (Jiang Wen), the real power behind the Emperor, enlists the aid of the greatest warrior in the land, Guan Yu (Donnie Yen). However, Guan Yu is a loyal friend of Cao Cao's enemy Liu Bei (Alex Fong) so to persuade the peerless warrior to fight, Cao Cao takes his beloved Qi Lan (Sun Li) hostage. After leading Cao Cao's forces to victory Guan Yu sets out with Qi Lan to rejoin Liu Bei. But now Cao Cao has deemed him too great a threat to live, and on the journey he must face all the forces at the Emperor's command sent to destroy him." year="2011-04-28" director="Alan Mak, Felix Chong Man-Keung" actors="Donnie Yen, Jiang Wen, Sun Li, Alex Fong, Shao Bing, Andy On, Wang Xuebing, Wang Bo-Chieh, Dong Yong, Li Zonghan",FR - The Lost Bladesman  (2011)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=559424.mkv&play_token=NAX58kNXVh&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/oPlNLXkMFWryGh1P3nA7EIHIQ2n.jpg" group-title="|FR| GUERRE" tvg-type="movie" description="Un soldat américain quitte l'amour de sa vie pour infiltrer les lignes allemandes et tuer Hitler. Des décennies plus tard, ce dernier est confronté à un tout autre ennemi, un authentique Bigfoot issu des montagnes canadiennes." year="2019-02-08" director="Robert D. Krzykowski" actors="Sam Elliott, Aidan Turner, Caitlin Fitzgerald, Rizwan Manji, Larry Miller, Ron Livingston, Nikolai Tsankov, Ellar Coltrane, Sean Bridgers, Kelley Curran",FR - The Man Who Killed Hitler and Then the Bigfoot  (2019)
