#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="http://103.176.90.118/images/movies//g9enfTHBAw652S2e48JkQTMKft6.jpg" group-title="|FR| GUERRE" tvg-type="movie" description="Revient sur la jeunesse et les années d’apprentissage du célèbre auteur J.R.R. Tolkien. Orphelin, il trouve l’amitié, l’amour et l’inspiration au sein d’un groupe de camarades de son école. Mais la Première Guerre Mondiale éclate et menace de détruire cette « communauté ». Ce sont toutes ces expériences qui vont inspirer Tolkien dans l’écriture de ses romans de la Terre du Milieu 'Bilbo le Hobbit' et 'Le Seigneur des Anneaux'." year="2019-05-03" director="Fox Searchlight Pictures, TSG Entertainment, Chernin Entertainment" actors="N/A",FR - Tolkien (2019)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=236129.mkv&play_token=jnnEMTQuzM&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/cUGYzkxQ55y5NaR3AgW7xsJw8MX.jpg" group-title="|FR| GUERRE" tvg-type="movie" description="1950, en pleine guerre de Corée, une opération menée par le général Douglas MacArthur s'opère sur la ville portuaire d'Incheon afin de sécuriser l'endroit. Les troupes de l'ONU sont majoritairement composées de Marines américains dont l'âge moyen est de dix-sept ans et n'ayant suivi que deux semaines d'entraînement avant de partir sur le front. La bataille d'Incheon marque un tournant décisif qui a inversé le cours de la guerre contre les forces du Nord soutenues par les communistes (Armée populaire de Corée) jusqu'à la reprise de la ville de Séoul." year="2019-09-25" director="Kwak Kyung-taek, Kim Tae-hun" actors="Kim Myung-min, Choi Min-ho, Kim Sung-cheol, Kim In-kwon, Kwak Si-yang, Lee Jae-wook, Jang Ji-gun, Lee Ho-jung, Dong Bang-woo, George Eads",FR - Battle of Jangsari  (2019)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=231826.mkv&play_token=n46UVlKoMI&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/lDlovumILImYpNXmbDTA3uwzkql.jpg" group-title="|FR| GUERRE" tvg-type="movie" description="1942, la France est sous l’occupation nazie. Charlotte Gray, jeune écossaise recrutée comme agent secret, se joint à la Résistance. Son but réel : secourir celui qu’elle aime, engagé dans la Royal Air Force. Dans un monde où tout est secret, elle réalise très vite qu’elle ne peut faire confiance qu’à elle-même…" year="2001-12-17" director="Gillian Armstrong" actors="Cate Blanchett, Billy Crudup, Michael Gambon, Rupert Penry-Jones, Anton Lesser, James Fleet, Abigail Cruttenden, Charlotte McDougall, Robert Hands, Nicholas Farrell",FR - Charlotte Gray (2001)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=229832.mp4&play_token=BRK2uQBYaQ&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/78hDh9EHDMbox4FlKlOrRfrmgpU.jpg" group-title="|FR| GUERRE" tvg-type="movie" description="A group of military elite from the U.S., Russia, UK, China and France join forces to fight an elite underground terrorist network." year="2019-10-04" director="Mike Gunther" actors="Stephen Lang, Will Yun Lee, Chris Mulkey, Rory Markham, Roman Mitichyan, Jermaine Love, Bertrand-Xavier Corbi, Katie Keene, Fernando Chien, Michael Blalock",FR - Rogue Warfare  (2019)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=214873.mkv&play_token=whhfTNeRsL&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/qe3YDHYlv7wYRwAaHwUL0L5USaH.jpg" group-title="|FR| GUERRE" tvg-type="movie" description="De nos jours, à Leningrad, Nastya, une vielle femme, est interviewée par une équipe de télévision. Elle raconte ses souvenirs de la Seconde Guerre mondiale. Elle revient notamment sur ses jeunes années, en septembre 1941, dans une Leningrad qui venait d'être assiégée par les Allemands, et sur son histoire d'amour avec Kostya Gorelov, un jeune cadet. Pendant ce temps, l'armée soviétique tente d'organiser l'évacuation de plusieurs centaines de personnes d'une ville de deux millions d'habitants, qui pourrait bientôt être frappée par la famine." year="2019-01-31" director="Alexey Kozlov" actors="Mariya Melnikova, Andrey Mironov-Udalov, Gela Meskhi, Anastasiya Melnikova, Sergey Zharkov, Ivan Lyrchikov, Valeriy Degtyar, Mikhail Morozov, Nikolay Gorshkov, Evgeniya Lyubimova",FR - Saving Leningrad  (2019)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=214880.mkv&play_token=mDVMlXPxLk&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/hJRvrrBPSDV6PbE4xek3mUt2Cfq.jpg" group-title="|FR| GUERRE" tvg-type="movie" description="The next installment of the Rogue Warfare Trilogy. Daniel has been captured and it is up to the TEAM to find him before it is to late." year="2019-12-02" director="Mike Gunther" actors="Will Yun Lee, Stephen Lang, Chris Mulkey, Fernando Chien, Essam Ferris, Bertrand-Xavier Corbi, Rory Markham, Gina DeCesare",FR - Rogue Warfare: The Hunt  (2019)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=213431.mkv&play_token=EFo8yPPXEB&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/hj8pyoNnynGeJTAbl7jcLZO8Uhx.jpg" group-title="|FR| GUERRE" tvg-type="movie" description="The story of the Battle of Midway, and the leaders and soldiers who used their instincts, fortitude and bravery to overcome massive odds." year="2019-11-06" director="Roland Emmerich" actors="Ed Skrein, Patrick Wilson, Woody Harrelson, Luke Evans, Mandy Moore, Luke Kleintank, Dennis Quaid, Aaron Eckhart, Keean Johnson, Nick Jonas",FR - Midway  (2019)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=208551.mkv&play_token=mu3UM2ioXs&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/3DNZnzuLzUCIcfQZZz4gT7epvx7.jpg" group-title="|FR| GUERRE" tvg-type="movie" description="1988-1989. The end of the Soviet-Afghan war. The USSR begins its withdrawal from Afghanistan. Soviet General Vasiliev's son - a pilot named Alexander gets kidnapped by the mujahideen after his airplane crashes. As a result the 108th motorized infantry division's long awaited return home gets put on hold for one last mission: bring the General's son back. Based on true events the previously untold story of the courageous and tragic withdrawal campaign (through the Salang pass) reveals the danger the horror and the complexity of human nature during wartime." year="2019-05-10" director="Pavel Lungin" actors="Kirill Pirogov, Yan Tsapnik, Vitaly Kishchenko, Fyodor Lavrov, Oleg Vasilkov, Anton Momot, Mikhail Kremer, Alexander Kuznetsov, Kirill Ermichev, Roman Kolotukhin",FR - Leaving Afghanistan  (2019)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=207099.mkv&play_token=z8BgT1a42C&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/8u0QBGUbZcBW59VEAdmeFl9g98N.jpg" group-title="|FR| GUERRE" tvg-type="movie" description="England, 15th century. Hal, a capricious prince who lives among the populace far from court, is forced by circumstances to reluctantly accept the throne and become Henry V." year="2019-10-11" director="David Michôd" actors="Timothée Chalamet, Joel Edgerton, Sean Harris, Tom Glynn-Carney, Lily-Rose Depp, Thomasin McKenzie, Robert Pattinson, Ben Mendelsohn, Andrew Havill, Dean-Charles Chapman",FR - The King (2019)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=207113.mkv&play_token=ScY9v4RmYV&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/6LlqyjAik3Kh68QQ9AchSJEF0Z5.jpg" group-title="|FR| GUERRE" tvg-type="movie" description="Major Ronan Jackson (Devon Sawa), an accomplished fighter pilot for the Israel Defense Forces and son of a U.S. Senator (Robert Patrick), is shot down while flying through Syrian airspace. After miraculously surviving the crash, Jackson is taken captive by a group of Hezbollah militiamen. A gripping and powerful story packed with hard-hitting action, Jarhead: Law of Return follows a squad of elite soldiers, led by Gunnery Sergeant Dave Torres (Amaury Nolasco), as they risk their own lives in the hopes of saving an ally they've never met." year="2019-10-01" director="Don Michael Paul" actors="Yael Eitan, Nicholas Aaron, Devon Sawa, Ben Cross, Amaury Nolasco, Robert Patrick, Tsahi Halevi, Shanti Ashanti, Jeff Pierre, Udi Razzin",FR - Jarhead: Law of Return  (2019)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=205499.mkv&play_token=DZZjibNTAt&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/7GsM4mtM0worCtIVeiQt28HieeN.jpg" group-title="|FR| GUERRE" tvg-type="movie" description="A World War II satire that follows a lonely German boy whose world view is turned upside down when he discovers his single mother is hiding a young Jewish girl in their attic. Aided only by his idiotic imaginary friend, Adolf Hitler, Jojo must confront his blind nationalism." year="2019-10-18" director="Taika Waititi" actors="Roman Griffin Davis, Thomasin McKenzie, Scarlett Johansson, Taika Waititi, Sam Rockwell, Rebel Wilson, Alfie Allen, Stephen Merchant, Archie Yates, Luke Brandon Field",FR - Jojo Rabbit  (2019)
