#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/vblJ5cTqZKg3DSyN1z8JxTUyf2Y.jpg" group-title="|FR| GUERRE" tvg-type="movie" description="19-year-old Billy Lynn is brought home for a victory tour after a harrowing Iraq battle. Through flashbacks the film shows what really happened to his squad - contrasting the realities of war with America's perceptions." year="2016-11-10" director="Ang Lee" actors="Joe Alwyn, Kristen Stewart, Chris Tucker, Garrett Hedlund, Vin Diesel, Steve Martin, Makenzie Leigh, Ismael Cruz Córdova, Arturo Castro, Ben Platt",FR - Billy Lynn's Long Halftime Walk  (2016)
