#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/ebqttF1Vjgde6uSFBEw9mta7Hd3.jpg" group-title="|FR| PARAMOUNT+" tvg-type="movie" description="When the 'Heart Eyes Killer' strikes Seattle, a pair of co-workers pulling overtime on Valentine's Day are mistaken for a couple by the elusive couple-hunting killer. Now, they must spend the most romantic night of the year running for their lives." year="2025-02-06" director="Josh Ruben, Lauren Sick, Julie-Anne Mueller, Joe Nolan, Laurie Wright" actors="Olivia Holt, Mason Gooding, Gigi Zumbado, Michaela Watkins, Devon Sawa",FR - Heart Eyes (2025)
